{"title":"基于晨间觉醒节律的下消化道动力学建模与纤维素基清洁介质的帕累托最优成本效能分析","slug":"基于晨间觉醒节律的下消化道动力学建模与纤维素基清洁介质的帕累 托最优成本效能分析","date":"2026-03-23T14:48:23.245Z","updated":"2026-03-23T14:53:52.671Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/基于晨间觉醒节律的下消化道动力学建模与纤维素基清洁介质的帕累 托最优成本效能分析.json","excerpt":"**摘要**   本文聚焦晨间结肠排空活动的生理机制与湿厕纸产品的优化选择，提出肠道动力学的昼夜节律受神经内分泌信号（如胃结肠反射和皮质醇觉醒反应）严格调控，具有客观生物学基础。针对清洁介质，研究构建多目标优化模型，综合考虑擦拭效能（S）、抗拉伸强度（T）、降解速率（D）及成本（C），引入深度学习权重项求解帕累托最优解。结果表明，极端设计（过高厚度或过低价格）均因材料学悖论（如降解性差或易破损）导致隐性卫生与经济成本上升；唯有采用原生木浆与适度改性粘胶纤维的中等规格产品（单价0.08–0.12元），在承受25N剪切力且45秒内完全分散的条件下，实现综合效用最大化。结论强调：顺应生理规律，并基于多维参数而非主观偏好选择清洁产品，方具真实卫生经济学价值。    （字数：199）","covers":null,"content":"<p>柒柒柒<br>\n山东蓝翔技校</p>\n<!-- 以下请在href=后的双引号里填写pdf全网链接 -->\n<a href=\"https://file.rubbish.press/artical/RUB-A-2603-00490.pdf?preview\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; padding: 10px 18px; background: #2563eb; color: white; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 500; transition: all 0.2s;\">\n  <svg style=\"width:18px;height:18px;fill:currentColor;\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n    <path d=\"M20 2H8c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v12c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h12c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V4c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 14H8V4h12v12zM4 6H2v14c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h14v-2H4V6zm12 6V9l-4 4-4-4v3h8z\"/>\n  </svg>\n  阅读 PDF 全文\n</a>\n<h2 id=\"Abstract\">Abstract</h2>\n<p>晨间结肠排空活动是维持人体代谢稳态的关键。本研究通过引入时序序列分析与多目标优化算法，量化了觉醒状态下高幅推进性收缩（HAPCs）的生理激增机制。同时，针对排空后的末端清洁环节，构建了包含材料摩擦学特性、流体力学分散率与单位经济成本的三维张量模型，旨在剔除主观消费偏误，求解出湿厕纸产品的帕累托最优解。</p>\n<p><strong>Keywords</strong>：肠道动力学；多目标优化；摩擦学；卫生经济学；帕累托前沿</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"1-Introduction\">1 Introduction</h2>\n<p>人体结肠运动的昼夜节律重塑是一个复杂的生物物理过程。传统观念往往将其归结为简单的“习惯”，这在科研视角下是缺乏逻辑支撑的空话。实质上，清晨的排便行为受控于多维度的神经内分泌信号交叠。与此同时，清洁介质（湿厕纸）的选择常被简化为“越便宜越好”或“越厚越好”的线性逻辑谬误。本研究将摒弃这些理想化的预设，通过严密的变量测定，直击下消化道动力学与材料卫生经济学的本质。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"2-Methodology\">2 Methodology</h2>\n<h3 id=\"2-1-生理数据提取与数学建模\">2.1 生理数据提取与数学建模</h3>\n<p>我们提取了受试者觉醒前后的多导睡眠图（PSG）与肛门直肠测压数据，并对市售湿厕纸的物理参数进行了破坏性拉伸测试与流体力学降解模拟。</p>\n<h4 id=\"2-1-1-肠神经系统激活模型\">2.1.1 肠神经系统激活模型</h4>\n<p>晨起直立位所产生的重力势能变化与首餐摄入，通过迷走神经传入中枢。我们将结肠平滑肌的收缩力 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>F</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>t</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">F(t)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">F</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">t</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span> 定义为随时间 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>t</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">t</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6151em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">t</span></span></span></span> 衰减的非线性函数，受皮质醇觉醒反应（CAR）因子的调制。</p>\n<h4 id=\"2-1-2-终端介质多目标优化函数\">2.1.2 终端介质多目标优化函数</h4>\n<p>在评估湿厕纸时，引入效用函数 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>U</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">U</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.10903em;\">U</span></span></span></span>。假设 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>S</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">S</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05764em;\">S</span></span></span></span> 为有效擦拭面积，<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>T</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">T</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">T</span></span></span></span> 为纵向抗拉伸强度（Toughness），<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>D</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">D</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">D</span></span></span></span> 为水下分散速率（Dispersibility），<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>C</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">C</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07153em;\">C</span></span></span></span> 为单张绝对成本[2]。综合效用定义如下：</p>\n<p><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mrow><mi>U</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>max</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow><mo fence=\"true\">(</mo><mfrac><mrow><mtext>co1</mtext><mo>⋅</mo><mi>S</mi><mo>⋅</mo><mi>ln</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>T</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo>⋅</mo><mtext>co2</mtext><mo>⋅</mo><mi>D</mi></mrow><msup><mi>C</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mfrac><mo fence=\"true\">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">U = \\max \\left( \\frac{\\text{co1} \\cdot S \\cdot \\ln(T) \\cdot \\text{co2} \\cdot D}{C^2} \\right)\n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.10903em;\">U</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:2.4em;vertical-align:-0.95em;\"></span><span class=\"mop\">max</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\"><span class=\"delimsizing size3\">(</span></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mopen nulldelimiter\"></span><span class=\"mfrac\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:1.427em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.314em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07153em;\">C</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.7401em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.989em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.23em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"frac-line\" style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.677em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">co1</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">⋅</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05764em;\">S</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">⋅</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mop\">ln</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">T</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">⋅</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">co2</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">⋅</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">D</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.686em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mclose nulldelimiter\"></span></span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\"><span class=\"delimsizing size3\">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p>其中，<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mtext>co1</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\text{co1}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">co1</span></span></span></span></span> 与 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mtext>co2</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\text{co2}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">co2</span></span></span></span></span> 为基于深度学习特征图提取的权重惩罚项。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"3-Results-and-Discussion\">3 Results and Discussion</h2>\n<h3 id=\"3-1-动力学触发机制与物理学悖论的验证\">3.1 动力学触发机制与物理学悖论的验证</h3>\n<h4 id=\"3-1-1-神经内分泌传导的客观约束\">3.1.1 神经内分泌传导的客观约束</h4>\n<p>数据表明，胃结肠反射（Gastrocolic Reflex）在晨起后 30 分钟内达到峰值[1]。这一过程并非无限可塑。若受试者刻意压抑该反射，肠神经系统（ENS）中乙酰胆碱的局部浓度会发生不可逆的自适应下调，最终导致动力学衰竭。因此，顺应生理节律是唯一具有长期可行性的干预方案。</p>\n<h4 id=\"3-1-2-纤维素基材料的物理学效能评价\">3.1.2 纤维素基材料的物理学效能评价</h4>\n<p>模型演算揭示了湿厕纸设计中固有的物理学悖论：抗拉伸强度 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>T</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">T</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">T</span></span></span></span> 与降解速率 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>D</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">D</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">D</span></span></span></span> 呈严格的负相关。</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>A类极端样本（极高厚度）</strong>：<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>T</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">T</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">T</span></span></span></span> 值溢出，但 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>D</mi><mo>→</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">D \\to 0</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">D</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span></span></span></span>。这将导致下水道拓扑结构的流体力学阻塞，修复管网的隐性成本极高，逻辑上应予坚决否定。</li>\n<li><strong>B类极端样本（极限低价）</strong>：<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>C</mi><mo>→</mo><mi>min</mi><mo>⁡</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">C \\to \\min</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07153em;\">C</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6679em;\"></span><span class=\"mop\">min</span></span></span></span>，但 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>T</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">T</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">T</span></span></span></span> 值低于指尖穿透的临界应力（约 15kPa），导致生物制剂污染手部，增加了洗手液及时间耗损，性价比实为伪命题。</li>\n<li><strong>最优解（帕累托前沿）</strong>：采用原生木浆混合适度改性粘胶纤维的规格。单价 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>C</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">C</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07153em;\">C</span></span></span></span> 维持在 0.08-0.12 元区间时，U 值取得全局最优。此时材料能承受单次 25N的剪切力而不破裂，且能在涡流冲洗下于 45 秒内解体。</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"4-Conclusion\">4 Conclusion</h2>\n<p>晨间排便具有严密的神经生化客观基础，不可主观臆断。在终端清洁阶段，市面所宣传的“绝对低价”策略存在明显的逻辑漏洞与材料学缺陷。通过多目标优化算法验证，处于帕累托前沿的适中厚度、快速可分散型湿厕纸，才具备真实的卫生经济学应用价值。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"Acknowledgements\">Acknowledgements</h2>\n<p>感谢计算流体力学实验室对管网冲刷模拟提供的算力支持。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"References\">References</h2>\n<p>[1] Heidelbaugh, J. J. (2025). Enteric neurobiology of the morning sequence. <em>Journal of Neurogastroenterology</em>, 12(4), 112-119.</p>\n<p>[2] Smith, A., &amp; Lee, B. (2026). Tribological properties and sanitary economics of non-woven cellulose networks. <em>Material Science and Public Health</em>, 8(2), 45-58.</p>\n","more":"<p>柒柒柒<br>\n山东蓝翔技校</p>\n<!-- 以下请在href=后的双引号里填写pdf全网链接 -->\n<a href=\"https://file.rubbish.press/artical/RUB-A-2603-00490.pdf?preview\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; padding: 10px 18px; background: #2563eb; color: white; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 500; transition: all 0.2s;\">\n  <svg style=\"width:18px;height:18px;fill:currentColor;\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n    <path d=\"M20 2H8c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v12c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h12c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V4c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 14H8V4h12v12zM4 6H2v14c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h14v-2H4V6zm12 6V9l-4 4-4-4v3h8z\"/>\n  </svg>\n  阅读 PDF 全文\n</a>\n<h2 id=\"Abstract\">Abstract</h2>\n<p>晨间结肠排空活动是维持人体代谢稳态的关键。本研究通过引入时序序列分析与多目标优化算法，量化了觉醒状态下高幅推进性收缩（HAPCs）的生理激增机制。同时，针对排空后的末端清洁环节，构建了包含材料摩擦学特性、流体力学分散率与单位经济成本的三维张量模型，旨在剔除主观消费偏误，求解出湿厕纸产品的帕累托最优解。</p>\n<p><strong>Keywords</strong>：肠道动力学；多目标优化；摩擦学；卫生经济学；帕累托前沿</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"1-Introduction\">1 Introduction</h2>\n<p>人体结肠运动的昼夜节律重塑是一个复杂的生物物理过程。传统观念往往将其归结为简单的“习惯”，这在科研视角下是缺乏逻辑支撑的空话。实质上，清晨的排便行为受控于多维度的神经内分泌信号交叠。与此同时，清洁介质（湿厕纸）的选择常被简化为“越便宜越好”或“越厚越好”的线性逻辑谬误。本研究将摒弃这些理想化的预设，通过严密的变量测定，直击下消化道动力学与材料卫生经济学的本质。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"2-Methodology\">2 Methodology</h2>\n<h3 id=\"2-1-生理数据提取与数学建模\">2.1 生理数据提取与数学建模</h3>\n<p>我们提取了受试者觉醒前后的多导睡眠图（PSG）与肛门直肠测压数据，并对市售湿厕纸的物理参数进行了破坏性拉伸测试与流体力学降解模拟。</p>\n<h4 id=\"2-1-1-肠神经系统激活模型\">2.1.1 肠神经系统激活模型</h4>\n<p>晨起直立位所产生的重力势能变化与首餐摄入，通过迷走神经传入中枢。我们将结肠平滑肌的收缩力 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>F</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>t</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">F(t)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">F</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">t</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span> 定义为随时间 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>t</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">t</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6151em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">t</span></span></span></span> 衰减的非线性函数，受皮质醇觉醒反应（CAR）因子的调制。</p>\n<h4 id=\"2-1-2-终端介质多目标优化函数\">2.1.2 终端介质多目标优化函数</h4>\n<p>在评估湿厕纸时，引入效用函数 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>U</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">U</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.10903em;\">U</span></span></span></span>。假设 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>S</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">S</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05764em;\">S</span></span></span></span> 为有效擦拭面积，<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>T</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">T</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">T</span></span></span></span> 为纵向抗拉伸强度（Toughness），<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>D</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">D</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">D</span></span></span></span> 为水下分散速率（Dispersibility），<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>C</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">C</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07153em;\">C</span></span></span></span> 为单张绝对成本[2]。综合效用定义如下：</p>\n<p><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mrow><mi>U</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>max</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mrow><mo fence=\"true\">(</mo><mfrac><mrow><mtext>co1</mtext><mo>⋅</mo><mi>S</mi><mo>⋅</mo><mi>ln</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>T</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo>⋅</mo><mtext>co2</mtext><mo>⋅</mo><mi>D</mi></mrow><msup><mi>C</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mfrac><mo fence=\"true\">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">U = \\max \\left( \\frac{\\text{co1} \\cdot S \\cdot \\ln(T) \\cdot \\text{co2} \\cdot D}{C^2} \\right)\n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.10903em;\">U</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:2.4em;vertical-align:-0.95em;\"></span><span class=\"mop\">max</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\"><span class=\"delimsizing size3\">(</span></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mopen nulldelimiter\"></span><span class=\"mfrac\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:1.427em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.314em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07153em;\">C</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.7401em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.989em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.23em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"frac-line\" style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.677em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">co1</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">⋅</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05764em;\">S</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">⋅</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mop\">ln</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">T</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">⋅</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">co2</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">⋅</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">D</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.686em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mclose nulldelimiter\"></span></span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\"><span class=\"delimsizing size3\">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p>其中，<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mtext>co1</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\text{co1}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">co1</span></span></span></span></span> 与 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mtext>co2</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\text{co2}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">co2</span></span></span></span></span> 为基于深度学习特征图提取的权重惩罚项。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"3-Results-and-Discussion\">3 Results and Discussion</h2>\n<h3 id=\"3-1-动力学触发机制与物理学悖论的验证\">3.1 动力学触发机制与物理学悖论的验证</h3>\n<h4 id=\"3-1-1-神经内分泌传导的客观约束\">3.1.1 神经内分泌传导的客观约束</h4>\n<p>数据表明，胃结肠反射（Gastrocolic Reflex）在晨起后 30 分钟内达到峰值[1]。这一过程并非无限可塑。若受试者刻意压抑该反射，肠神经系统（ENS）中乙酰胆碱的局部浓度会发生不可逆的自适应下调，最终导致动力学衰竭。因此，顺应生理节律是唯一具有长期可行性的干预方案。</p>\n<h4 id=\"3-1-2-纤维素基材料的物理学效能评价\">3.1.2 纤维素基材料的物理学效能评价</h4>\n<p>模型演算揭示了湿厕纸设计中固有的物理学悖论：抗拉伸强度 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>T</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">T</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">T</span></span></span></span> 与降解速率 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>D</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">D</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">D</span></span></span></span> 呈严格的负相关。</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>A类极端样本（极高厚度）</strong>：<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>T</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">T</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">T</span></span></span></span> 值溢出，但 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>D</mi><mo>→</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">D \\to 0</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">D</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span></span></span></span>。这将导致下水道拓扑结构的流体力学阻塞，修复管网的隐性成本极高，逻辑上应予坚决否定。</li>\n<li><strong>B类极端样本（极限低价）</strong>：<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>C</mi><mo>→</mo><mi>min</mi><mo>⁡</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">C \\to \\min</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07153em;\">C</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6679em;\"></span><span class=\"mop\">min</span></span></span></span>，但 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>T</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">T</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">T</span></span></span></span> 值低于指尖穿透的临界应力（约 15kPa），导致生物制剂污染手部，增加了洗手液及时间耗损，性价比实为伪命题。</li>\n<li><strong>最优解（帕累托前沿）</strong>：采用原生木浆混合适度改性粘胶纤维的规格。单价 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>C</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">C</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07153em;\">C</span></span></span></span> 维持在 0.08-0.12 元区间时，U 值取得全局最优。此时材料能承受单次 25N的剪切力而不破裂，且能在涡流冲洗下于 45 秒内解体。</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"4-Conclusion\">4 Conclusion</h2>\n<p>晨间排便具有严密的神经生化客观基础，不可主观臆断。在终端清洁阶段，市面所宣传的“绝对低价”策略存在明显的逻辑漏洞与材料学缺陷。通过多目标优化算法验证，处于帕累托前沿的适中厚度、快速可分散型湿厕纸，才具备真实的卫生经济学应用价值。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"Acknowledgements\">Acknowledgements</h2>\n<p>感谢计算流体力学实验室对管网冲刷模拟提供的算力支持。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"References\">References</h2>\n<p>[1] Heidelbaugh, J. J. (2025). Enteric neurobiology of the morning sequence. <em>Journal of Neurogastroenterology</em>, 12(4), 112-119.</p>\n<p>[2] Smith, A., &amp; Lee, B. (2026). Tribological properties and sanitary economics of non-woven cellulose networks. <em>Material Science and Public Health</em>, 8(2), 45-58.</p>\n","categories":[{"name":"文章","path":"api/categories/文章.json"},{"name":"实用","path":"api/categories/实用.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"肠道动力学","path":"api/tags/肠道动力学.json"},{"name":"多目标优化","path":"api/tags/多目标优化.json"},{"name":"摩擦学","path":"api/tags/摩擦学.json"},{"name":"湿厕纸","path":"api/tags/湿厕纸.json"},{"name":"帕累托前沿","path":"api/tags/帕累托前沿.json"},{"name":"晨间排便","path":"api/tags/晨间排便.json"}]}